      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or age. Meticulously maintained with a full service history, it runs perfectly and offers a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a truly top-tier vehicle.",
