    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest signs of use and character from its time on the road, it remains a solid and dependable choice for anyone needing a functional ride. It's a great opportunity to own a well-loved car at a fantastic value!",
