    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work or serve as a donor for parts. The exterior shows its age with several deep dents, failing clear coat, and noticeable rust bubbling along the wheel arches and rocker panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears and persistent odors. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission exhibits slipping, meaning it is not currently reliable for daily transport and should likely be towed from the lot.",
