    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which represents a premier choice for the discerning driver. This model demonstrates a commitment to excellence, featuring a well-preserved interior and a powertrain that delivers consistent, reliable performance. Every aspect of this automobile has been inspected to ensure it meets our professional standards for safety and aesthetic appeal. Offering a sophisticated driving experience and exceptional long-term value, this vehicle stands as a testament to quality automotive care.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
