      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and has been well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how great it feels behind the wheel!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is routed through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis has been properly sorted, including proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a recent cooling system refresh. The VANOS system is quiet and the valve clearances have been recently calibrated, ensuring the valvetrain remains sharp. While showing honest wear consistent with its age, the mechanical fundamentals\u2014including the suspension bushings and braking system\u2014are robust, offering the precise turn-in and balanced weight distribution this platform is celebrated for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 29000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-documented car that has been treated with respect. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, typical of careful daily use. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean; the leather seats are supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All technological features, including the infotainment screen, backup camera, and heated seats, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs quietly, having benefited from a recent full synthetic oil change and a new air filter. The brakes feel firm, and the suspension provides a composed, rattle-free ride. The car sits on a set of premium all-season tires with plenty of life left. This is a non-smoker vehicle with a clean title, ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
